0d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影包括六段故事 1850年，南太平洋，美國公證人亞當&middot;尤因（吉姆&middot;斯特吉斯Jim Sturgess 飾）在船上被不明寄生蟲病折磨，他用日記記錄下自己所見所聞；1931年，蘇格蘭，落魄青年羅伯特&middot;弗羅比舍（本&middot;衛肖Ben Whishaw 飾）為音樂大師記錄曲譜，受到半本旅行日記的啟發創作出了恢宏壯闊的《雲圖六重奏》；1975年，美國加州，小報記者路易莎&middot;雷（哈莉&middot;貝瑞Halle Berry 飾）冒著生命危險調查一樁核電站醜聞...<br />\n<br />\n2.<img src=\"https://s3.beautimode.com/upload/media/96617c4d12775d9a8b5ca0164ba0cf2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.beautimode.com%2Fupload%2Fmedia%2F96617c4d12775d9a8b5ca0164ba0cf2a.jpg&h=bff7f8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10 45PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=5672668e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=e04b1c33\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51519b2387e098868b6bb987ca7842f0528645f0","tid":2193100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  第二套係薯片版"},{"pid":"54dee5dd8b904036bb64d8c326de7ab3c227c6e2","tid":2193100,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets